descriptionHtml:
April Fools 2013 joke, fills all the major towns and cities with aggressive horkers.  Originally titled \"Super Cities Enhanced - Add More Life to Skyrim\" and given the following description:

\"Ever feel lonely in Skyrim? Feel that there\'s not enough variety in towns, like there\'s more bandits in the world than there are citizens? Then this is the mod for you. This mod adds many meticulously hand-placed things to the major towns and cities of Skyrim to give them more life and variety and enrich your immersion and gameplay experience!\"
author: BLOODGAZMS
